{{- define "lineage.k8s-at-home" -}}
This chart is built on the [k8s-at-home common library](https://github.com/k8s-at-home/library-charts)
(v4). Most configuration keys (`image`, `env`, `service`, `ingress`,
`persistence`, ...) follow its schema, so the library supports more than what
is spelled out in `values.yaml`.
{{- end -}}

{{- define "lineage.bjw-s" -}}
This chart is built on the [bjw-s-labs common library](https://github.com/bjw-s-labs/helm-charts).
Most configuration keys (`controllers`, `service`, `ingress`, `persistence`,
...) follow its schema; see the [common library documentation](https://bjw-s-labs.github.io/helm-charts/docs/)
for everything it supports beyond what is spelled out in `values.yaml`.
{{- end -}}

