## TL;DR

```shell
helm repo add obeone https://charts.obeone.cloud
helm repo update
helm install {{ template "chart.name" . }} obeone/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

## About

{{ template "custom.app" . }}

- **Application:** {{ template "custom.link.app" . }}
- **Container image:** {{ template "custom.link.image" . }}{{ template "custom.links.extra" . }}
- **Chart source:** [`charts/{{ template "chart.name" . }}`](https://github.com/obeone/charts/tree/main/charts/{{ template "chart.name" . }})

## Prerequisites

- Helm 3
- A Kubernetes cluster matching the chart's `kubeVersion` constraint (see [`Chart.yaml`](./Chart.yaml))
{{- template "custom.prerequisites" . }}

## Configuration

{{ template "custom.lineage" . }}

Defaults are meant to work out of the box on any cluster. The full list of
options lives in [`values.yaml`](./values.yaml), is validated by
[`values.schema.json`](./values.schema.json) at install time, and is documented
in the [Values](#values) section below. Override it with your own values file:

```shell
helm install {{ template "chart.name" . }} obeone/{{ template "chart.name" . }} -f my-values.yaml
```
{{- template "custom.configuration" . }}

## Upgrading

```shell
helm repo update
helm upgrade {{ template "chart.name" . }} obeone/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

Each release lists its changes in the
[Artifact Hub changelog](https://artifacthub.io/packages/helm/obeone/{{ template "chart.name" . }}?modal=changelog);
give it a look before jumping across several chart versions.

## Uninstalling

```shell
helm uninstall {{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

PersistentVolumeClaims created by the chart are kept around: delete them
manually if you also want the data gone.

{{ template "chart.requirementsSection" . }}

{{ template "chart.valuesSection" . }}

## Verifying the chart signature

Charts in this repository are signed with GPG and every release ships a
provenance file. The public key is available at
[`charts.obeone.cloud/public_key.gpg`](https://charts.obeone.cloud/public_key.gpg),
fingerprint `B9FE852F28888D27F8C9A11CD33E04CD22E335CE`.

```shell
# Import the signing key into a legacy keyring (helm verifies with GnuPG v1 keyrings)
curl -fsSL https://charts.obeone.cloud/public_key.gpg | gpg --import
gpg --export > ~/.gnupg/pubring.gpg

# Pull the chart and check it against its provenance file
helm pull --verify obeone/{{ template "chart.name" . }}
```

## Support

This is a personal chart repository, maintained on a best-effort basis. Bug
reports and contributions are welcome on
[GitHub](https://github.com/obeone/charts/issues).

